      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''This society does not see migrants as human beings, it sees them as criminals.''</p>
        <p>LUCÍA DEL CARMEN BERMÚDEZ, a Mexican government official, on Central Americans who cross its southern border. [12]</p>
